= Inter-Party Relationships

SLD cannot rebuild the left alone. Which relationship should the party invest in?

- @relation_ko: Improve working relations with PO/KO circles.
- @relation_psl: Keep channels open with PSL.
- @relation_tw: Work with Twój Ruch, Greens, and liberal-left remnants.
- @relation_razem: Open channels to the emerging new left.
- @relation_alone: Stand alone for now.

@relation_ko
subtitle: -1 resources
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
on-arrival: {!
Q.resources -= 1;
Q.party_resources = Q.resources;
Q.ko_relation += 5 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.ko_trzaskowski_strength = Math.min(10, Q.ko_trzaskowski_strength + 0.2);
Q.sld_apparatus_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.sld_apparatus_dissent - 0.2);
Q.tr_residue_dissent = Math.min(10, Q.tr_residue_dissent + 0.2);
!}

The practical case for anti-PiS cooperation is obvious, even before PiS returns to power.

- @post_event: Continue.

@relation_psl
subtitle: -1 resources
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
on-arrival: {!
Q.resources -= 1;
Q.party_resources = Q.resources;
Q.psl_relation += 5 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.rural_west_left += 0.6 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.catholic_nonpracticing_left += 0.4 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.sld_modernizers_dissent = Math.min(10, Q.sld_modernizers_dissent + 0.2);
!}

The PSL channel is unglamorous but useful: local government, rural credibility, and future coalition arithmetic.

- @post_event: Continue.

@relation_tw
subtitle: -1 resources
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
on-arrival: {!
Q.resources -= 1;
Q.party_resources = Q.resources;
Q.tr_residue_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.tr_residue_dissent - 0.5);
Q.tr_residue_strength = Math.min(10, Q.tr_residue_strength + 0.3);
Q.unaffiliated_left += 0.7 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.lgbtq_left += 0.7 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.sld_apparatus_dissent = Math.min(10, Q.sld_apparatus_dissent + 0.2);
!}

The Palikot wave is already fading, but its secular-liberal voters and activists still matter.

- @post_event: Continue.

@relation_razem
subtitle: -1 resources
view-if: year >= 2015
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
on-arrival: {!
Q.resources -= 1;
Q.party_resources = Q.resources;
Q.razem_relation += 5 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.pps_up_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.pps_up_dissent - 0.3);
Q.sld_apparatus_dissent = Math.min(10, Q.sld_apparatus_dissent + 0.4);
Q.under_30_left += 0.6 * (1 - Q.dissent);
!}

The new left is suspicious of the SLD's inheritance, but early contact may prevent a complete split of the anti-PO left electorate.

- @post_event: Continue.

@relation_alone

The party avoids new entanglements this month.

- @post_event: Continue.

@international_relations
title: International Relations
new-page: true
