max-visits: 6

= Party Organizations

The party is more than a Sejm club. It needs local structures, publications, youth work, and social links.

- @org_media: Fund party media and journalists.
- @org_welfare: Fund legal aid and social-support work.
- @org_culture: Fund conferences, clubs, and political education.
- @org_unions: Invest in union linkage.
- @org_youth: Support young activists.
- @org_regional: Rebuild regional structures.
- @org_nothing: Do not increase funding.

@org_media
subtitle: -1 resources
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
on-arrival: resources -= 1; party_resources = resources; media_timer = 0
go-to: media

@org_welfare
subtitle: -1 resources
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
on-arrival: {!
Q.resources -= 1;
Q.party_resources = Q.resources;
Q.civil_society_capital = Math.min(10, Q.civil_society_capital + 0.4);
Q.urban_working_class_left += 1.0 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.women_over_50_left += 0.5 * (1 - Q.dissent);
!}

The SLD backs legal aid and social support around evictions, labor disputes, and local welfare offices.

- @post_event: Continue.

@org_culture
subtitle: -1 resources
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
on-arrival: {!
Q.resources -= 1;
Q.party_resources = Q.resources;
Q.sld_apparatus_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.sld_apparatus_dissent - 0.4);
Q.sld_modernizers_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.sld_modernizers_dissent - 0.4);
Q.tr_residue_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.tr_residue_dissent - 0.4);
Q.pps_up_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.pps_up_dissent - 0.4);
Q.left_brand_strength = Math.min(10, Q.left_brand_strength + 0.2);
!}

Political education and cultural work make members feel part of something larger than electoral arithmetic.

- @post_event: Continue.

@org_unions
subtitle: -1 resources
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
on-arrival: {!
Q.resources -= 1;
Q.party_resources = Q.resources;
Q.ip_union_strength = Math.min(10, Q.ip_union_strength + 0.3);
Q.civil_society_capital = Math.min(10, Q.civil_society_capital + 0.3);
Q.urban_working_class_left += 1.1 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.pps_up_strength = Math.min(10, Q.pps_up_strength + 0.3);
Q.pps_up_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.pps_up_dissent - 0.3);
!}

The party tries to reconnect with labor without pretending that old union ties are enough by themselves.

- @post_event: Continue.

@org_youth
subtitle: -1 resources
