Q.unaffiliated_left += 0.7 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.sld_modernizers_strength = Math.min(10, Q.sld_modernizers_strength + 0.4);
Q.sld_apparatus_dissent = Math.min(10, Q.sld_apparatus_dissent + 0.3);
!}

New activists bring energy, but not all of them are interested in deference to the old party hierarchy.

- @post_event: Continue.

@org_regional
