Q.sld_apparatus_strength = Math.min(10, Q.sld_apparatus_strength + 0.4);
Q.rural_west_left += 0.9 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.urban_working_class_left += 0.7 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.left_campaign_bonus += 0.2 * (1 - Q.dissent);
!}

Councillors, district offices, and people who can still fill a room are the SLD's most concrete assets.

- @post_event: Continue.

@org_nothing

The party avoids new organizational spending.

- @post_event: Continue.

@media
title: Media
new-page: true
