= Media

The SLD has old press habits, television veterans, and a weak online presence. What should the media operation do?

- @media_commercial: Broaden appeal through television-friendly messaging.
- @media_campaign: Focus media on electing left deputies.
- @media_ideological: Open space for internal ideological debate.
- @media_digital: Build digital channels.
- @post_event: Do nothing with media at the moment.

@media_commercial
on-arrival: {!
Q.resources += 1;
Q.party_resources = Q.resources;
Q.media_reach = Math.min(10, Q.media_reach + 0.4);
Q.urban_professionals_left += 0.8 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.catholic_nonpracticing_left += 0.5 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.tr_residue_dissent = Math.min(10, Q.tr_residue_dissent + 0.5);
Q.pps_up_dissent = Math.min(10, Q.pps_up_dissent + 0.3);
!}

The party sounds more accessible and raises money, but activists dislike the flattening of the message.

- @post_event: Continue.

@media_campaign
on-arrival: {!
Q.media_reach = Math.min(10, Q.media_reach + 0.3);
Q.urban_working_class_left += 0.9 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.age_50_65_left += 0.7 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.left_campaign_bonus += 0.2 * (1 - Q.dissent);
!}

The media line is simple: save the left in parliament.

- @post_event: Continue.

@media_ideological
on-arrival: {!
Q.sld_apparatus_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.sld_apparatus_dissent - 0.5);
Q.sld_modernizers_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.sld_modernizers_dissent - 0.5);
Q.tr_residue_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.tr_residue_dissent - 0.5);
Q.pps_up_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.pps_up_dissent - 0.5);
Q.left_brand_strength = Math.min(10, Q.left_brand_strength + 0.1);
!}

The party papers and friendly outlets let factions argue in public without immediately breaking the organization.

- @post_event: Continue.

@media_digital
subtitle: -1 resources
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
on-arrival: {!
Q.resources -= 1;
Q.party_resources = Q.resources;
Q.media_reach = Math.min(10, Q.media_reach + 0.8);
Q.under_30_left += 1.0 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.unaffiliated_left += 0.7 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.sld_modernizers_strength = Math.min(10, Q.sld_modernizers_strength + 0.3);
!}

Online work cannot repair the whole brand, but it starts reaching voters the SLD usually misses.

- @post_event: Continue.

@rally
title: Political Rally
new-page: true
is-card: true
card-image: img/party_cards/political_rally.png
tags: lewica_party_affairs
view-if: rally_timer <= 0
on-arrival: month_actions += 1; rally_timer = 6; rally_timer = 2 if (year = 2015 and month >= 8)

= Political Rally

Mass rallies and conventions still matter, especially near an election. What is the theme?

- @rally_class: Wages, labor, and public services.
- @rally_secular: A secular state.
- @rally_democracy: Defending democracy against PiS.
- @rally_europe: European social democracy.
- @rally_local: A mixture of local concerns.

@rally_class
on-arrival: {!
Q.urban_working_class_left += 1.6 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.under_30_left += 0.5 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.pps_up_strength = Math.min(10, Q.pps_up_strength + 0.3);
Q.pps_up_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.pps_up_dissent - 0.3);
Q.ko_relation -= 1;
!}

The rally makes the party sound materially left again.

- @post_event: Continue.

@rally_secular
on-arrival: {!
Q.secularization_tide = Math.min(10, Q.secularization_tide + 0.3);
Q.unaffiliated_left += 1.3 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.lgbtq_left += 1.0 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.catholic_practicing_left -= 0.3;
Q.vatican_episcopate_alignment = Math.max(0, Q.vatican_episcopate_alignment - 0.3);
!}

The party gives secular voters something unmistakable to vote for.

- @post_event: Continue.

@rally_democracy
on-arrival: {!
Q.constitutional_crisis_risk = Math.max(0, Q.constitutional_crisis_risk - 0.1);
Q.ko_relation += 1;
Q.urban_professionals_left += 0.8 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.catholic_nonpracticing_left += 0.5 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.pis_relation -= 1;
!}

The rally puts the SLD inside the anti-PiS democratic camp.

- @post_event: Continue.

@rally_europe
on-arrival: {!
Q.eu_institutional_alignment = Math.min(10, Q.eu_institutional_alignment + 0.2);
Q.urban_professionals_left += 0.9 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.under_30_left += 0.5 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.ko_relation += 1;
Q.sld_modernizers_strength = Math.min(10, Q.sld_modernizers_strength + 0.2);
!}

The SLD wraps itself in Europe and social-democratic normalcy.

- @post_event: Continue.

@rally_local
on-arrival: {!
Q.urban_working_class_left += 1.0 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.rural_west_left += 0.8 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.age_65_plus_left += 0.5 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.left_regional_rebuild += 0.2;
Q.left_campaign_bonus += 0.15 * (1 - Q.dissent);
!}

The speakers follow the mood of local audiences: hospitals, buses, rents, jobs, pensions.

- @post_event: Continue.

@civil_society
title: Civil Society Linkage
new-page: true
