= Civil Society Linkage

In this setting, the old paramilitary slot becomes organized civil society: unions, women's groups, watchdogs, and anti-far-right networks.

- @civil_unions: Work through union networks.
- @civil_women: Support women's organizations.
- @civil_watchdogs: Support democratic watchdogs.
- @civil_antifascist: Support anti-far-right monitoring.
- @civil_nothing: Keep the linkage informal.

@civil_unions
subtitle: -1 resources
choose-if: resources >= 1
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
