Q.resources -= 1;
Q.party_resources = Q.resources;
Q.civil_society_capital = Math.min(10, Q.civil_society_capital + 0.5);
Q.ip_union_strength = Math.min(10, Q.ip_union_strength + 0.4);
Q.urban_working_class_left += 1.0 * (1 - Q.dissent);
Q.pps_up_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.pps_up_dissent - 0.3);
!}

The SLD stops treating unions as ceremonial partners and starts using them as live political infrastructure.

- @post_event: Continue.

