Q.secularization_tide = Math.min(10, Q.secularization_tide + 0.2);
Q.sld_apparatus_dissent = Math.min(10, Q.sld_apparatus_dissent + 0.2);
!}

The pre-Black-Protest infrastructure is still scattered, but the SLD can begin building trust.

- @post_event: Continue.

@civil_watchdogs
