@party_disunity
title: Party Disunity
new-page: true
is-card: true
card-image: img/party_cards/party_disunity.png
tags: lewica_party_affairs
view-if: party_disunity_timer <= 0 and (left_dissent >= 4 or sld_apparatus_dissent >= 7 or sld_modernizers_dissent >= 7 or gawkowski_network_dissent >= 7 or tr_residue_dissent >= 7 or pps_up_dissent >= 7)
on-arrival: month_actions += 1; party_disunity_timer = 4
frequency: 200

= Party Disunity

The party is being pulled apart by factional dissatisfaction. Something must be done to keep the SLD functional.

[? if sld_apparatus_dissent >= 7: The apparatus is angry. ?]
[? if sld_modernizers_dissent >= 7: The modernizers are angry. ?]
[? if gawkowski_network_dissent >= 7: Gawkowski's secretariat network is angry. ?]
[? if tr_residue_dissent >= 7: The Twój Ruch residue is angry. ?]
[? if pps_up_dissent >= 7: The socialist junior partners are angry. ?]

- @disunity_enforce: Enforce party discipline.
- @disunity_apparatus: Give concessions to the apparatus.
- @disunity_modernizers: Give concessions to the modernizers.
- @disunity_gawkowski: Give procedural room to Gawkowski's network.
- @disunity_tr: Give concessions to Twój Ruch liberals.
- @disunity_pps: Give concessions to PPS/UP socialists.
- @disunity_do_nothing: Let the factions argue.

@disunity_enforce
on-arrival: {!
Q.sld_apparatus_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.sld_apparatus_dissent - 0.8);
Q.sld_modernizers_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.sld_modernizers_dissent - 0.8);
Q.gawkowski_network_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.gawkowski_network_dissent - 0.8);
Q.tr_residue_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.tr_residue_dissent - 0.8);
Q.pps_up_dissent = Math.max(0, Q.pps_up_dissent - 0.8);
Q.urban_working_class_left -= Q.dissent * 1.0;
Q.urban_professionals_left -= Q.dissent * 0.8;
Q.under_30_left -= Q.dissent * 0.8;
!}

Discipline reduces dissent, but it can look like the old machine crushing debate.

- @post_event: Continue.

@disunity_apparatus
view-if: sld_apparatus_dissent >= 7
on-arrival: sld_apparatus_dissent -= 1.5; sld_modernizers_dissent += 0.8; tr_residue_dissent += 0.6

The leadership promises more control to regional structures and veteran organizers.

- @post_event: Continue.

@disunity_modernizers
view-if: sld_modernizers_dissent >= 7
on-arrival: sld_modernizers_dissent -= 1.5; sld_apparatus_dissent += 0.8; gawkowski_network_strength += 0.2

The party promises a more contemporary message and gives modernizers more public space.

- @post_event: Continue.

@disunity_gawkowski
view-if: gawkowski_network_dissent >= 7
on-arrival: gawkowski_network_dissent -= 1.5; gawkowski_network_strength += 0.3; sld_apparatus_dissent += 0.5; sld_modernizers_dissent -= 0.3

The leadership gives the secretary general more procedural control over branches, candidate lists, and internal consultation.

- @post_event: Continue.

@disunity_tr
view-if: tr_residue_dissent >= 7
on-arrival: tr_residue_dissent -= 1.5; sld_apparatus_dissent += 0.5; pps_up_dissent += 0.4

The party gives secular-liberal allies more room.

- @post_event: Continue.

@disunity_pps
view-if: pps_up_dissent >= 7
on-arrival: pps_up_dissent -= 1.5; sld_modernizers_dissent += 0.5

The party makes programmatic concessions to the old socialist partners.

- @post_event: Continue.

@disunity_do_nothing
on-arrival: sld_apparatus_dissent += 0.2; sld_modernizers_dissent += 0.2; gawkowski_network_dissent += 0.2; tr_residue_dissent += 0.2; pps_up_dissent += 0.2

Perhaps dissent is healthy. Perhaps it is just drift.

- @post_event: Continue.
